lass=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">out</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">of</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">bounds</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">memory</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">access</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/FiveMovesAhead/wasmi_mem_issue\">Here is the repo with code to replicate the issue</a></p>\n<p>Am I doing anything obviously wrong? The same issue also occurs with <code>wasmi</code></p>\n</blockquote>",
